(I found it to be toxic and although I am quite good I grew to hate the tedious practicing) In the last month ive discovered a passion for creating music. It's always been there, but now is not blocked by stress for the need to practice classical. i hear all these jazz and funky music ideas in my head. but when i go to play them my muscle memory in my hands just reverts to a classical style.
